reviewText: Disappointed on a variety of levels. For starters this DVD is only Episodes 8-13, which was (at time of purchase) not clear in the listing. Also, much of the content seems to be repeats of hunts features in Drury's previous 'Whitetail Madness' and 'Dream Season' DVDs (which they have unfortunately stopped after 18 seasons). There is also increased product placement for Under Armor, Biologic, and others...
